		///                          const Uint8 * mask,
		///                          int w, int h, int hot_x,
		///                          int hot_y);
		/// </code><para>                                                                                                            </para><br /><b>## Version ##</b><para>This function is available since SDL 3.0.0.</para><br /><b>## Code Examples ##</b><code>/* Stolen from the mailing list */
		/// /* Creates a new mouse cursor from an XPM */
