		///         <para>"force" - Always use the RIFF chunk size as a boundary for the chunksearch.</para>
		///       </description>
		///     </item>
		///     <item>
		///       <description>
		///         <para>"ignorezero" - Like "force", but a zero size searches up to 4 GiB.(default)</para>
		///       </description>
		///     </item>
		///     <item>
		///       <description>
